<para style="p">For the chief musician; on stringed instruments. A maschil of David; when the Ziphites came and said to Saul, "Does David not hide himself with us?"</para>

<para style="b" />

<para style="q1">

<verse number="1" style="v" />Save me, God, by your name,</para>

<para style="q1">and judge me in your might.</para>

<para style="q1">

<verse number="2" style="v" />Hear my prayer, God;</para>

<para style="q1">give ear to the words of my mouth.</para>

<para style="q1">

<verse number="3" style="v" />For strangers have risen up against me,</para>

<para style="q1">and pitiless men have sought after my life;</para>

<para style="q1">they have not set God before them.

<char style="qs">Selah</char></para>
